---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Kalyan AI | AI systems built around your business"
	description="Why Kalyan AI builds AI systems around how each business works, with owner control and ongoing support after delivery."
>
	<main class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-5xl flex-col gap-10 px-6 pb-14">
		<section class="ka-card mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">About Kalyan AI</h1>
			<p class="copy-narrow max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg text-[var(--primary)]">We build AI systems that make your business easier to run and grow.</p>
			<p class="copy-narrow max-w-3xl mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">Kalyan AI exists because useful AI is not a fixed product you drop into a company. It has to be shaped around how the business works, where decisions are made, and where the right system can have the biggest impact.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-4 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<div class="mx-auto aspect-[4/4.5] w-full max-w-md overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] shadow-sm">
				<img
					class="h-full w-full object-cover"
					src="/images/1761512653.png"
					alt="Zax Kalyan"
					loading="lazy"
					decoding="async"
					style="object-position: 50% 12%;"
				/>
			</div>

			<div class="space-y-3 text-center">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Founder</h2>
				<div class="space-y-3 !text-center">
					<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)] text-center">I'm Zax Kalyan, founder of Kalyan AI. I've spent 15+ years leading and growing businesses under real-world pressure, owning P&amp;L, building teams, and delivering results across industries.</p>
					<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)] text-center">Before Kalyan AI, I started using AI systems inside my own businesses to support the work that mattered: reporting, customer communication, marketing content, finance tasks, and day-to-day operating decisions.</p>
					<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)] text-center">The useful part was not the technology by itself. It was having systems that understood the business context and supported better decisions without taking control away from the owner.</p>
					<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)] text-center">I'm also a contributor and shareholder at Nuvo Labs, a deep-tech AI research company. That keeps us close to what is coming next, while staying focused on what matters day to day: reliability, usefulness, and measurable business impact.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Built around the business</h2>
			<div class="space-y-2 !text-center">
				<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">We learn how your business runs before deciding what the system should do. That includes the tools, data, people, approvals, edge cases, and decisions that shape the real operating environment.</p>
				<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">The result is not a generic layer added on top. It is a system designed around the work it needs to support.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Owner control matters</h2>
			<div class="space-y-2 !text-center">
				<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">It is your business, your decisions. We make sure the system behind it supports you properly.</p>
				<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">That means clear ownership, explicit approvals where they matter, traceable actions, and people involved when judgment is needed.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-4 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">We stay involved</h2>
			<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">A serious business system needs more than a handover. We host, monitor, support, and improve systems as real usage shows what needs adjusting.</p>
			<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">That ongoing involvement helps the system remain useful as the business changes.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-4 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Different from fixed products</h2>
			<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">Fixed products expect the business to adapt to them. Generic automation often connects tasks without enough thought about ownership, risk, exceptions, or long-term support.</p>
			<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">Kalyan AI is built around controlled delivery. Every serious system is scoped, risk-assessed, tested beyond the happy path, documented, deployed carefully, and supported after go-live.</p>
			<a href="/how-we-build/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-[var(--primary)] text-[var(--primary)] rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-[var(--primary)] hover:text-white transition-colors">See how we build</a>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card p-8 my-16 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)] mb-6">Why hosted?</h2>
			<p class="text-[var(--muted)] mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Because you want the system to keep working, not another technical responsibility to manage.</p>
			<ul class="space-y-3 text-[var(--muted)]">
				<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-3"><span class="text-[var(--primary)]">✓</span> Reliability: monitored, maintained, and supported so issues are not left to drift.</li>
				<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-3"><span class="text-[var(--primary)]">✓</span> Security and control: least-privilege access, clear data boundaries, and traceability.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">How we work</h2>
			<ol class="space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)] text-center list-none">
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Discover -</span> understand how the business runs today, the data involved, and the key decisions.</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Build -</span> implement the first high-impact phase with safeguards and clear ownership.</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Deploy -</span> launch with you, monitor outcomes, and stabilise fast.</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Improve -</span> refine the system based on real usage and business feedback.</li>
			</ol>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">What you get</h2>
			<ul class="space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)] text-center list-none">
				<li>A working system shaped around a real business need</li>
				<li>Integration into your current tools where the project calls for it</li>
				<li>Ongoing hosting, monitoring, and improvements</li>
				<li>Training so your team can use it from day one</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">What you can expect</h2>
			<ul class="space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)] text-center list-none">
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Clarity</span> on who decides what, and what happens next</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Momentum</span> without losing control</li>
				<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Reliability</span> from a system that is maintained and supported</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<div class="text-center">
			<a
				class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-[var(--secondary)]"
				href="/contact#book"
				data-plausible="BookACall"
			>
				Book a conversation
			</a>
		</div>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">FAQs</h2>
			<div class="divide-y divide-[var(--border-subtle)] rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border-subtle)] bg-white/80 text-center">
				{[
					{
						q: 'What types of businesses do you work with?',
						a: 'Owner-led organisations where the right AI system can support decisions, customers, operations, or growth without taking control away from the people running the business.',
					},
					{
						q: 'How quickly can we ship a first version?',
						a: 'Most first versions are delivered in 2-4 weeks once we have access to the right people, examples, and systems. We keep the initial scope tight to show value early.',
					},
					{
						q: 'Do you host the system for us?',
						a: 'Yes. We host, monitor, and maintain the system so you do not need extra infrastructure or support staff to keep it reliable.',
					},
					{
						q: 'What about data security and access control?',
						a: 'We set clear data boundaries, least-privilege access, and audit trails. Ownership and permissions stay defined for your team.',
					},
					{
						q: 'Can this connect to our existing tools and processes?',
						a: 'Yes. We integrate with your current systems and processes where that is the right way to make the system fit how you already work.',
					},
					{
						q: 'How do pricing and ongoing support work?',
						a: 'We scope a build fee for the first version, then provide a hosting and support plan that covers monitoring, fixes, and iterative improvements.',
					},
					{
						q: 'What do you need from us to get started?',
						a: 'Access to the people, examples, and systems that show how you work today, plus a clear owner for decisions. We handle the build and support around that.',
					},
				].map((item) => (
					<details class="group px-4 py-3 text-[var(--muted)]">
						<summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-center gap-2 text-center text-[var(--brand-navy)] font-semibold transition hover:text-[var(--brand-navy-light)] focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-[var(--primary)] focus-visible:ring-offset-0">
							<span>{item.q}</span>
							<span class="text-sm text-[var(--muted)] group-open:rotate-45 transition">+</span>
						</summary>
						<div class="pt-2 text-[var(--muted)] text-center">
							<p>{item.a}</p>
						</div>
					</details>
				))}
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
